### Submit invoice
POST http://localhost:8000/submit
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=inspection

--inspection
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="region"

US
--inspection
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="submitter_email"

inspector@example.com
--inspection
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="mock_invoice.txt"
Content-Type: text/plain

INVOICE 1048
Supplier: Northline Freight Services
Fleet: Commercial tractor trailer
Vehicle VIN: 1FT8W3BT9NEC00001
Bill of Lading: BOL-99128
Cargo: Palletized inspection equipment
--inspection--

### Review approval
POST http://localhost:8000/review/{{job_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "action": "APPROVE",
  "comments": "Documents satisfy inspection policy."
}

